title: NCT Dream’s Renjun Features In New Teaser Photos For “My First And Last”
text:
NCT Dream has now shared a new set of teaser images for their comeback! 
After previously releasing teasers that feature members Chenle and Jisung , the NCT sub-unit has revealed a new series of teasers for both the group and member Renjun, as well as a duo shot with Renjun and Jeno. 
Like his fellow members before him, Renjun looks adorable in both a uniform for formal shots and a retro-inspired and colorful casual outfit at school in his teasers! 
NCT Dream’s first mini album entitled “My First and Last” is due out on February 9 at midnight KST.
